Package io.proximax.sdk.model.account.props

Enum AccountPropertyType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AccountPropertyType>
      • io.proximax.sdk.model.account.props.AccountPropertyType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AccountPropertyType>
    public enum AccountPropertyType
extends java.lang.Enum<AccountPropertyType>
    Account property type 0x01 The property type is an address. 0x02 The property type is mosaic id. 0x03 The property type is a transaction type. 0x04 Property type sentinel. 0x80 + type The property is interpreted as a blocking operation.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      ALLOW_ADDRESS
